There were 3 other sightings in Dublin on or around October 23rd 2008
Summary: Me and 3 others saw three big Orange lights that were hovering about 100 feet above the ground
divs: Sighting DetailsMyself and three other people were riding our horses and were near a single story barn. After we passed the barn we saw three Big orange lights in a row. They were at an angle and moving about 30-4- miles an hour from the West to the North and they were about 100 feet off the ground. The lights were blinking on and off as they moved. We saw the lights for about five minutes. Then all the lights flash off and it was gone.
